extends ../templates/layout.jade
block head
  meta(property='og:title' content='#{graphic._post.title}')
  meta(property='og:site_name' content='Start Essential')
  meta(property='og:url' content='http://startessential.com/preview/#{graphic.short_code}')
  meta(property='og:description' content='#{graphic._post.content}')
  meta(property='og:image' content='#{graphic.custom_image.normal.Location}')
block body
  div#preview
    if sid
      include ../templates/_header.jade
    else
      include ../templates/_header-signup.jade
    main.main
      if sid
        section.tools
          .tools-inner
            a(href='/posts') < Back to all graphics
      .main-content
        .graphic
          .graphic-inner.cf
            .graphic-image-wrap.no-overlay
              .pinit
                a(href="//www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/" data-pin-do="buttonBookmark"  data-pin-color="red" data-pin-height="28")
                  img(src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pinit_fg_en_rect_red_28.png")
              img.graphic-image(src=graphic.custom_image.original.Location)
            .graphic-details
              h1.details-title= graphic._post.title
              .details-content
                if graphic._post.content
                  | !{graphic._post.content_rendered}
                else
                  p
                    i No description for now
              if sid
                if sid._id == graphic._user._id
                  .share-facebook.details-link(data-code='http://startessential.com/preview/#{graphic.short_code}') Share on Facebook
                  a.details-download(href=graphic.custom_image.original.Location target='_blank') Download
        .tour
          .tour-inner.cf
            article.tour-copy
              h2.tour-label Discover a Simple, Healthier Life
              h5.tour-sub-header It's changed the lives of millions, now it's your turn
              section
                p Ever since I started using essential oils, they have made life-changing differences that I love to share with others. Don't be afraid to jump in and start the journey! I am so thankful I made that decision, and I would be thrilled to help you personally discover them for yourself. Please, take a moment to read about them and begin your journey towards a healthier wellbeing.
              section
                h4 What are essential oils?
                p An essential oil is an aromatic, concentrated oil that is extracted from flowers, shrubs, and other plants. It has an unique, complex chemistry that beautifully balances and contributes to a healthy body. By addressing root issues and imbalances on a cellular level, essential oils are able to support the body in resisting diseases and malfunctions it faces on a daily and long-term basis.
              section
                h4 How can you use essential oils?
                p Using essential oils, especially on a day-to-day basis, is an incredibly exciting and simple process. Because Young Living essential oils are so concentrated and pure, it only takes a couple drops to start experiencing an oil's benefits. These drops can be diffused through your home, applied directly to the skin, or sometimes taken internally. It's such a tiny addition to your life, yet brings invaluable aspects to a healthy body.
              section
                h4 Why signup as a member with Young Living?
                p When ordering oils from young living, you can choose to be a Member or a Retail Customer. By choosing Member, you receive several discounts and benefits (24% off for one) and are simply asked to share and talk about the oils you love. Additionally, you may signup people with referral links to recieve a commision from their purchases. A Young Living membership is simply a family of people who love to share their successes and experiences with essential oils &mdash; something every oiler should be a part of.
            section.tour-signup
              .tour-signup-image-wrap
                img.tour-signup-image(src='/images/starter-kit-header.jpg' width='400')
              .tour-signup-inner
                h3.inner-title Get Your Own Oils
                p.inner-description Discovering essential oils is a key moment in millions of people's lives, and it begins with this complete starter kit. I will personally be there to educate you on how to use them and guide you to a healthier wellbeing!
                a.inner-signup(href=graphic._user.distributor_link) Signup with Young Living
block scripts
  script(src='/js/build/jquery.sticky-kit.min.js')
  script(type="text/javascript" async defer src="//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js")
